Docker

create a folder

mkdir (my-web-server)

cd my web.server

open the terminal.
touch index.html 
Enter

touch Dockerfile 
Enter

Open index file
copy small html code
Save

open Docker file and add
FROM httpd: 2.4

COPY index.html /usr/local/apache2/htdocs/

open terminal from folder
sudo docker build -t my-web-server.


Password

sudo docker run -p 8082:80 -d my-web-server

Enter

Generate hash code

open browser - http://localhost:8092

Type: localhost: 8082:80


Where -p port

      -d: detached mode
